Definition: providing carefully for the future
Example: wild squirrels are provident; a provident father plans for his children's education
Synonyms: noun, attribute, providence, verb, change, provide, IMPROVIDENT, FARSIGHTED, PRUDENT, THRIFTY, providing, carefully, for, the, future, wild, squirrels, are, provident, a, father, plans, his, children, s, education
Category: adj.all
